Package: evictionHotspots
Title: Spatial Identification of Eviction Hotspots Using Moran's I
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Oluwafisayo",
      family = "Ajayi",
      email = "oluwafisayo.ajayi@maine.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: 
    Tools for identifying and visualizing spatial eviction hotspots using 
    global and local spatial autocorrelation methods. The package computes 
    Global Moranâ€™s I and Local Indicators of Spatial Association (LISA) on 
    eviction-related variables within sf objects, constructs spatial 
    weights using k-nearest neighbors, and classifies statistically 
    significant local clusters. Visualization functions support both 
    static maps using tmap and interactive maps using leaflet.
